                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-grain">米、麵、油、烘焙</button></li>
                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-preserved">罐頭、醃漬食品、乾貨</button></li>
                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-sauce">調味料、醬料、湯</button></li>
                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-snack">零食、餅乾、甜品</button></li>
                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-frozen">冷凍、急凍食品</button></li>
                                <li><button type="button" class="header-nav-3-mega-tab" data-food-tab="fd-produce">水果、蔬菜</button></li>
